title: All The President's Trends 6/13: Rebel Wilson, Jennifer Hudson, Neo-Nazis, Mick Jagger, Crypto, Shaq
itunes:title: All The President's Trends 6/13: Rebel Wilson, Jennifer Hudson, Neo-Nazis, Mick Jagger, Crypto, Shaq
description:
In this edition of All The President's Trends, Jack and Miles discuss Rebel Wilson getting outed by the the Sydeny Morning Herald, Jennifer Hudson getting her EGOT, a bunch of neo-nazis getting arrested at Idaho Pride Festival, Mick Jagger getting COVID, Crypto crashing even deeper, and Shaq's early days on Inside the NBA!
